commitResults.messageTitle: Rename main class and add greeting
Add support for marking and unmarking tasks as done
Add support for different types of tasks
Change class hierarchy of the Task class and different types of tasks
commitResults.messageBody:
Instead of using an enum for task types, create separate classes
(Todo, Deadline, Event) that inherit from the abstract Task class.
This will make it easier to implement methods specific to each task
type later on.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add additional functionality for Deadline and Event tasks.
commitResults.messageBody:
Additional functionality allows the user to enter a deadline
and duraton for Deadline and Event tasks respectively, which
are stored in tasks in the task list.

Bug identified: all user input is stored and then displayed
in lower case, regardless of the initial capitalisation.
